import { Container, Nav, Navbar, NavDropdown } from "react-bootstrap";
import {LinkContainer} from 'react-router-bootstrap'
// import { Link, } from 'react-router-dom'; 

function Header() {
  return (
    <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" className="love" top variant="dark">
    <Container>
    <Navbar.Brand href="#home">SimexReact</Navbar.Brand>
    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
    <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
      <Nav className="m-auto">
        <LinkContainer to="/about">
            <Nav.link to="/add">About us</Nav.link>
        </LinkContainer>
        <NavDropdown title="Products" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">

          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Refill </NavDropdown.Item>
        </NavDropdown>
        <NavDropdown title="Resources" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Faq</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">learn</NavDropdown.Item>
        </NavDropdown>
      </Nav>
      <Nav>
        {/* <Link to="/add">Login</Link>
        <Link to="/add">
          Register
        </Link> */}
      </Nav>
    </Navbar.Collapse>
    </Container>
  </Navbar>
  );
}

export default Header
